# HR Portal Front-End (React + Bootstrap + Modular Theme System)

A modular, reskinnable front-end HR management interface built with React, React Router, Bootstrap, and a custom theme architecture. Features include employee management, leave request handling, responsive layout, reusable UI components, and a full theme layer for rapid rebranding.

