---

## ğŸ§© Features

### HR Dashboard
- Add employees (modal)
- Edit employees (modal)
- Delete employees (confirmation modal)
- Search/filter employees
- Review leave requests
- Approve / Deny leave
- Fully responsive tables
- Themed steel/graphite/hazard palette

### Employee Dashboard
- Update profile information
- Submit leave requests
- Modular form fields
- Themed card panels

---

## ğŸ–¥ï¸ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-------------|
| Front-End | React 19 (Vite) |
| Styling | Bootstrap 5 + Custom Theme |
| Routing | React Router 7 |
| Components | Fully modular React components |
| Theming | Custom palette + CSS overrides |

---

## ğŸ¨ Theme Palette (sci-fi industrial)

| Name | Hex | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| Steel | `#4A4F55` | panels & surfaces |
| Graphite | `#1A1C1F` | backgrounds, contrast |
| Hazard Yellow | `#E9C357` | highlights, CTAs |
| Emergency Red | `#C54139` | warnings, destructive actions |

---

## ğŸ”„ Reskinning
To completely rebrand the site, update only:

```
theme/color.css
theme/index.css
theme/overrides.css
theme/sections.css
theme/spacing.css
```

No React components must be changed.

---

## ğŸš€ Running the Project

### Install dependencies:
```
npm install
```

### Start dev server:
```
npm run dev
```

### Build for production:
```
npm run build
```

---

## ğŸ§­ Why This Architecture Works
- Easy to maintain
- Easy to rebrand
- Easy to expand (new pages, dashboards, modals)
- Reusable components for ANY future project
- Clean separation of concerns
- Fully responsive (Bootstrap grid)
